summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $7.50 from the general fund of the City of Seattle to be paid to Jessie M. Elliott Frasch, being the amount of taxes paid by her for 1915 on that portion of Tract 28, Rosenbaum's Springhill No. 1, an addition to the City of Seattle, deeded to the City of Seattle April 5, 1915, for street and highway purposes.
